            <p>1403. N. 19<hi rend="sup">th</hi>. St<lb/>
                May 30<hi rend="sup">th</hi>h&#47;89.<lb/></p>
            <p>Dear Dr Morais.<lb/></p>
            <p>This morning&#44; we&#45;&#45;<lb/> M<hi rend="sup">rs</hi>. Rosenbach and I&#45;&#45;<lb/> called at the home of<lb/> the children attending<lb/> the school in 9<hi rend="sup">th</hi> St.<lb/>  It seems M<hi rend="sup">rs</hi>. Van Raaf&#45;&#45;<lb/> &#40;that is the name as we<lb/> got it&#41; the teacher&#44; has<lb/> made efforts to get the<lb/> children to attend her<lb/> school.  She is from Palestine<lb/></p>
                
                <pb n="2"/>
            <p>and so are some of the<lb/> children&#39;s parents&#45;&#45;and<lb/> a convert to Christianity&#59;<lb/> her school consists of<lb/> Jewish children only&#45;&#45;<lb/>&#45;&#45;excepting one boy&#45;&#45;and<lb/> numbers 29.  The induce&#45;<lb/>ments offered are French<lb/> dancing&#44; sewing and&#44; clothing.<lb/>  Some of the people seemed<lb/> ignorant of the nature<lb/> of the school&#44; and had<lb/> not questioned their chil&#45;<lb/>dren on the subject.  A<lb/> M<hi rend="sup">rs</hi>. White of 513 South St<lb/> is more enlightened than<lb/> many others&#44; and appears<lb/> shocked at having sent<lb/> her children where they<lb/></p>
                
                <pb n="3"/>
            <p>were taught that Moses was Lord compared<lb/> with Jesus Christ &#38;c &#38;c.  Her children dis&#45;<lb/>continue&#44; at once&#44; and she has volunteered<lb/> her influence to remove others.  I am<lb/> inclined to think the <hi rend="underline">back bone</hi> of M<hi rend="sup">rs</hi>.<lb/> Van Raaf&#39;s <hi rend="underline">soul&#45;saving</hi> efforts is bent&#44; at<lb/> least.  We did not go to the school<lb/> as it was closed to day&#44; but&#44; will<lb/> on another day&#44; if necessary&#59; in fact<lb/> are curious to see and interview the<lb/> convert.  If you learn anything<lb/> further requiring our efforts&#44; please<lb/> inform us and oblige<lb/> Yours very truly<lb/> Clara Hahn.<lb/></p>
            </body>
